<!-- ============================================================
   snippets/why99-box.liquid
   Explains the ₹99 advance payment system
   ============================================================ -->

{%- assign advance = settings.advance_amount | default: '99' -%}
{%- assign remaining = product.price | minus: advance -%}
{%- assign city = settings.city | default: 'Hyderabad' -%}

<div class="why99-box">
  <div class="why99-title">💡 Why do we ask for ₹{{ advance }}?</div>
  <div class="why99-explanation">
    In the past, unverified customers placed fake orders for "timepass" — our delivery team would travel across
    {{ city }}, and the customer wouldn't answer the door. This wasted a lot of time and money. Genuine customers
    pay ₹{{ advance }} to confirm they are real. <strong>₹{{ advance }} is NOT extra</strong> — it is deducted from your final
    {{ product.price | money }} bill.
  </div>
  <div class="why99-steps">
    <div class="why99-step">
      <div class="w99-icon">1</div>
      <div><strong>Pay ₹{{ advance }} now</strong> — confirms you're genuine &amp; filters fake orders</div>
    </div>
    <div class="why99-step">
      <div class="w99-icon">2</div>
      <div>We call within <strong>30 minutes</strong> to confirm delivery time</div>
    </div>
    <div class="why99-step">
      <div class="w99-icon">3</div>
      <div>Delivery arrives — <strong>open &amp; fully check</strong> the product first</div>
    </div>
    <div class="why99-step">
      <div class="w99-icon">4</div>
      <div>Happy? Pay <strong>{{ remaining | money }} cash</strong>. Not satisfied? Full ₹{{ advance }} refund</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="why99-refund">
    ✅ Not satisfied? We take the product back. Full ₹{{ advance }} refunded. No questions, no drama.
  </div>
</div>
